campsite (3.4.1ubuntu1) stable; urgency=low

  Improvements
  ------------
  - CS-2197: CSRF (Cross-site request forgery) protection implemented
  - CS-2214: Multiple general UI changes and fixes
  - CS-2179: Number of parameters in the articles search list reduced
  - CS-2206: Improved session handling to avoid logged user session grabbing via CSRF attack

  Bugs Fixed
  ----------
  - CS-2171: On backup data restore the file system_preferences.php is now - deleted
  - CS-2176: The restore script no longer crashes if the files/images directory didn't exist in the package
  - CS-2177: Layout errors in the universal list solved
  - CS-2180: Campsite installer no longer crashes on Windows
  - CS-2183: Missing default admin permission sorted
  - CS-2184: Feedback function working correctly
  - CS-2186: Universal list now working if topic has " in title
  - CS-2201: Plugin installation difficulties solved
  - CS-2203: UTF strings show up properly in email notifications
  - CS-2205: User input is correctly filtered out
  - CS-2208: Field values now change correctly in the universal list
  - CS-2209: Pagination and sorting now working properly in staff-user-admin of campsite
  - CS-2219: Localizer now supports languages with different country code (e.g. zh_CN - simplified, zh_TW - traditional)

 -- Sourcefabric <campsite-support@lists.sourcefabric.org>  Mon, 02 Aug 2010 19:25:32 +0300

